snippet.title: Backbone Under The Magnifying Glass
snippet.description:
Jason Laster, Software Engineer at Etsy and core Marionette contributor, gives a preview of his 2014 BackboneConf talk. In it, he'll discuss the new Marionette Inspector and how to incorporate it into your development workflow.

Slides: http://mbx.cm/t/YGUSG

Jason's 2014 BackboneConf talk: http://goo.gl/0wBdrP

Sponsored by: http://www.infor.com
Marionette.js: http://marionettejs.com
Marionette Chat Room: https://gitter.im/marionettejs/backbone.marionette
Jason Laster: https://twitter.com/jasonlaster11
